---
// Character Consistency - Master Reference Generation
---
<div class="flex justify-center my-8 not-prose">
    <div class="node w-full max-w-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 border-t-4 border-t-amber-500 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-xl transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white text-lg">1. Master Reference Generation</h3>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-black uppercase mb-3 tracking-widest">The "Holy Grail" Seed</div>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Before any story generation, we generate a locked set of visual references using a specific seed.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Visual: The 3 Angles -->
            <div class="flex gap-3">
                {['Front', 'Side', '45Â°'].map(angle => (
                    <div class="w-16 h-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 rounded-lg p-2 flex flex-col items-center">
                        <div class="ref-frame w-full h-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-md relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-slate-400 dark:bg-slate-600 rounded-full mb-1"></div>
                            <div class="absolute bottom-0 w-10 h-6 bg-slate-400 dark:bg-slate-600 rounded-full translate-y-3"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mt-2 uppercase">{angle}</span>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .node {
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
    }
</style>
